<h1>Forgot your password? No biggie!</h1>
        
<p>
	To reset your password, click on the link below. Keep in mind, the link will 
	expire in two hours.
</p>

<p>
  If you did not request your password to be reset, ignore this email and your 
  password will remain as it is.
</p>
        
<%= link_to "Reset Password", 
						"http://localhost:3000/password-reset/#{@user.email}/#{@user.reset_token}" %>